umes, affecting BSE, Angel One, and Groww's earnings. BSE may be less impacted due to its revenue model and market share gains.","summary":"STT hike in Budget 2026 impacts derivatives trading, causing shares of BSE Ltd, Angel One, and Groww to drop 5-9%. Nifty 50 fell 2%.\nIncreased STT rates may reduce trading volumes, affecting BSE, Angel One, and Groww's earnings. BSE may be less impacted due to its revenue model and market share gains.","url":"https://www.livemint.com/market/mark-to-market/stt-hike-2026-union-budget-2026-11769941488329.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-01T17:09:29","source":"Livemint"},{"id":"464121","title":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman announced a hike in STT for futures trading in Budget 2026, raising it to 0.05% from 0.02%.\nStocks of BSE, Angel One, and Groww dropped up to 10%. Zerodha Co-founder raised concerns over increased tax burden on investors.","summary":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman announced a hike in STT for futures trading in Budget 2026, raising it to 0.05% from 0.02%.\nStocks of BSE, Angel One, and Groww dropped up to 10%. Zerodha Co-founder raised concerns over increased tax burden on investors.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/budget-2026-securities-transaction-tax-stt-rasied-futures-options-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-impact-19838207.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-01T12:15:29","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"444734","title":"BSE reports Sensex open interest surged from 1.7M to 6M contracts.\nThis rise is due to shifting weekly options expiry from Tuesday to Thursday.","summary":"BSE reports Sensex open interest surged from 1.7M to 6M contracts.\nThis rise is due to shifting weekly options expiry from Tuesday to Thursday.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T14:00:58","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"444121","title":"ANMI urges SEBI to extend equity-like market-making to CDS, aiming to foster competition and reduce MCX's dominance.\nMCX commands 99% of CDS; market-making could boost liquidity, lower bid-ask spreads,